      "index": 0,
      "text": "set channel \u0022log\u0022 call Capture",
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Cut 2 surface in PLang. A PLang \u0060write to %channelName%\u0060 step lands on the new\nactor.channel[name].Write(data) path \u2014 the registry no longer holds WriteText/WriteAsync,\nand the type-switch on channel.stream.@this moved onto the element as a virtual.\nWithout the assertion this was a no-assertion smoke test (tester v1 F7) \u2014 it would\npass even if the accessor path was unreachable. Routing through a goal channel and\nasserting on the captured value pins that the Write call actually reaches handler code.",
